item.title: Chinquapin Hunting
item.description: This week’s tune for Fiddling Friday is Chinquapin Hunting, played in the tuning of GDGD. This is a tune that I first learned from a YouTube video, and it was also the first video where I saw the one and only Rushad Eggleston.
